The '''master control signal''' was dispatched to all [[Battle droid/Legends|battle droids]] and warships of the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|CIS]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] by [[Sith Lord/Legends|Lord]] [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Vader]], who used this signal to deactivate the CIS's [[Separatist Droid Army/Legends|droid army]] and [[Confederate Navy/Legends|navy]] after he [[Mission to Mustafar/Legends|murdered]] the [[Separatist Council/Legends|Separatist Council]], thus paving the way for [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine's]] new [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].

